# makefile for CQL3D (f90 pointered version, with .f extensions)
# May/06:  makefile_lf95_ptr is system developed by Nikolay Ershov
#          to produce a Fortran 90 pointered version of the code,
#          rather than the Cray pointered version obtained with
#          makefile_lf95.  Comparison of these two makefiles shows
#          only differences are in four lines referring to doptr.py
#          and tmpptr.f.
#          The source code modifications are carried out with the
#          python script doptr.py in ./ptr, and additional files
#          in that subdirectory.
#          Please follow this scheme for modification in code storage,
#          so that the two pointering systems are carried forward.

